{"lemma":"ظِلْفِ","slug":"ظِلْفِ","root":"ظ.ل.ف","root_slug":"ظ-ل-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ل-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27622","n27624","n27625","n27626","n27632"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%90%D9%84%D9%92%D9%81%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cloven hoof, hoof of an artiodactyl (even-toed ungulate)."}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ðˤilf/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27622","headword_ar":"ظَلْفٌ","root":"Zlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", of ground, or land,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such as is rugged, that will not show any foot-mark;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalafN","text_ar":"ظَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, * M:) or so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifapN","text_ar":"ظَلِفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalufapN","text_ar":"ظَلُفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalafapN","text_ar":"ظَلَفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalafN","text_ar":"ظَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies ground"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as horses like to run upon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or (i. e. the last) a place"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated above the water and the mud;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifN","text_ar":"ظَلِفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) this last thus expl. by Ibn-'Abbád: (O:) or this last and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifapN","text_ar":"ظَلِفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to ISh, (TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalafN","text_ar":"ظَلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalafapN","text_ar":"ظَلَفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so accord. to a copy of the T, in which the authority is not mentioned,) signify ground, or land,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the foot-mark will not appear, and which is high and rugged:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and accord. to Fr, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifN","text_ar":"ظَلِفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifapN","text_ar":"ظَلِفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify ground, or land,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that will not show a foot-mark;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were prevented from doing so: (T, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZilofN","text_ar":"ظِلْفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in a copy of the T,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifN","text_ar":"ظَلِفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in the TA,) accord. to Fr, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of ground, or land: but accord. to IAar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is hard, and does not show a foot-mark; in which is no softness, so as to be difficult to him who walks upon it; nor sand, so that the camels would have their feet burnt upon it; nor stones, so that they would be chafed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abraded, in the soles of their feet, upon it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is also expl. (by IAar, TA) as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is rugged and hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of ground, or land: (T, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifapN","text_ar":"ظَلِفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high"},{"kind":"text","text":"ground, or land,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that will not show a foot-mark."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaliyfN","text_ar":"ظَلِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~alofu","text_ar":"الظَّلْفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~alafu","text_ar":"الظَّلَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as relating to the means of subsistence.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalofN","text_ar":"ظَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ineffectual, null,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allowable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba damuhu ZalofFA","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ دَمُهُ ظَلْفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, S, M, O, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalafFA","text_ar":"طَلَفًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, T, S, M, O, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaliyfFA","text_ar":"ظَلِيفًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalofFA","text_ar":"طَلْفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalafFA","text_ar":"طَلَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, O) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaliyfFA","text_ar":"طَلِيفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His blood went for nothing; as a thing of no account; ineffectually;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in vain; unretaliated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompensated by a mulct."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, T, S, M, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","T","O","TA","AA","M"]},{"entry_id":"n27624","headword_ar":"ظِلْفٌ","root":"Zlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufor","text_ar":"ظُفْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cloven hoof"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of any ruminant"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the bovine kind"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T;) [i. e.] it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an appertenance of the bovine kind"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the gazelle"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"antelope"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is to them like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufor","text_ar":"ظُفْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadam","text_ar":"قَدَم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to us:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) one says the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rijol","text_ar":"رِجْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadam","text_ar":"قَدَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man, and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfir","text_ar":"حَافِر"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horse, and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuf~","text_ar":"خُفّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel and of an ostrich, and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zilof","text_ar":"ظِلْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a bovine animal and of a sheep or goat [and the like]: (ISk, T, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZolaAfN","text_ar":"اَظْلَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuluwfN","text_ar":"ظُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1919},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZolaAf","text_ar":"اَظْلَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied, by 'Amr Ibn-Maadee-kerib, to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoofs of horses,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O,) as is said by Lth and Az and IF, by poetic license, (O,) metaphorically: (S, O:) and by El-Akhtal, metaphorically, to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feet of men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, IB, TA.) [Its dual is used in the K, in explanations of the words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEirapN","text_ar":"شَعِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oEaru","text_ar":"اَشْعَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the latter instance on the authority of Lh, as meaning The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two halves of a cloven hoof."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja$imotu A_ilayoka ZilofFA","text_ar":"جَشِمْتُ اـِلَيْكَ ظِلْفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not had the trouble of bringing to thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"so much as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hoof of a gazelle"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AZ, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j$m","text_ar":"جشم"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yaA^okuluhu biDirosK wayaTaw^uhu biZilofK","text_ar":"هُوَ يَاْكُلُهُ بِضِرْسٍ وَيَطَوُهُ بِظِلْفٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He eats it with a lateral tooth, and treads it with a cloven hoof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"app. meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  It is sometimes used as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cloven-hoofed animals."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu xuf~N walaA HaAfirN walaA ZilofN","text_ar":"لَهُ خُفٌّ وَلَا حَافِرٌ وَلَا ظِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He possesses not camels, nor horses"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asses"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mules, nor sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other cloven-hoofed beasts"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xf","text_ar":"خف"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  It also signifies [or implies] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making consecutive progressions"},{"kind":"text","text":"in walking and in other actions, (T, K,) or, accord. to the L, in a thing. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='ati AlA_ibilu EalaY ZilofK waAHidK","text_ar":"جَا=ءَتِ الاـِبِلُ عَلَى ظِلْفٍ وَاحِدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A, O, TA) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels came following one another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA. [See also a similar phrase voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuf~N","text_ar":"خُفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ganamu fulaAnK ZilofK waAHidK","text_ar":"غَنَمُ فُلَانٍ ظِلْفٍ وَاحِدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAHidK","text_ar":"وَاحِدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalafK","text_ar":"ظَلَفٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats, of such a one, have all of them brought forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one after another"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is suitable to the requirements"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man, and of a beast: (M:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an object of desire:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an object of want."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAba","text_ar":"اَصَابَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN Zilofahu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ ظِلْفَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one attained what was suitable to his requirements,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what he desired:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes one says the like of any beast that finds, or lights on, or meets with, that which he likes. (M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajadati Ald~aAb~apu ZilofahaA","text_ar":"وَجَدَتِ الدَّابَّةُ ظِلْفَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a prov., (M, O,) applied to him who finds the means of attaining that which he seeks; (Meyd;) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beast found what was suitable to its requirements;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what withheld it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from other things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and prevented its desire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA. [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov., ii. 807.]) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajadati Al$~aApu ZilofahaA","text_ar":"وَجَدَتِ الشَّاةُ ظِلْفَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat, found suitable pasturage, and therefore did not quit it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) a prov. mentioned by Fr; applied to him, of men and of beasts, that finds what is suitable to him. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN mino Zilofi Alganami","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ مِنْ ظِلْفِ الغَنَمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A country of such as are suitable to sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajada Zilofahu","text_ar":"وَجَدَ ظِلْفَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He found what he loved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what he desired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what was suitable to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) said of a man. (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA wajadotu Einodahu ZilofiY","text_ar":"مَا وَجَدْتُ عِنْدَهُ ظِلْفِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did not find with him the object of my want."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalofN","text_ar":"ظَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the middle of the paragraph. ―         -b2-  [In some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ilofu","text_ar":"الظِّلْفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~alafu","text_ar":"الظَّلَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as relating to the means of subsistence. And in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZilofuhaA","text_ar":"ظِلْفُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifuhaA","text_ar":"ظَلِفُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalifu Aln~afosi","text_ar":"ظَلِفُ النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["T","M","S","O","Msb","K","ISk","TA","A"]},{"entry_id":"n27625","headword_ar":"ظَلَفٌ","root":"Zlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[as an inf. n.: see 1, last quarter. ―         -b2-  Also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarseness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the means of subsistence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, K:) thus the word is correctly written: not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zilof","text_ar":"ظِلْف"},{"kind":"text","text":", as we find it written in [copies of] the K: [nor"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalof","text_ar":"ظَلْف"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the CK:] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalafu AlEayo$i","text_ar":"ظَلَفُ العَيْشِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad., (O, TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straitness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarseness, of the means of subsistence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalofN","text_ar":"ظَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places, near the beginning of the paragraph.       -A3-  And see the last sentence of that paragraph. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anything that is easy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of light estimation, paltry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"despicable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalafN","text_ar":"طَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~u hayonK","text_ar":"كُلُّ هَيْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~u hay~inK","text_ar":"كُلُّ هَيِّنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZilofN","text_ar":"ظِلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter half. ―         -b2-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zaliyfap","text_ar":"ظَلِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27626","headword_ar":"ظَلِفٌ","root":"Zlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalofN","text_ar":"ظَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", former half, in three places.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalifu Aln~afosi","text_ar":"ظَلِفُ النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [accord. to the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalofu Aln~afosi","text_ar":"ظَلْفُ النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this is a mistranscription,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~afosi","text_ar":"النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zaliyfu","text_ar":"ظَلِيفُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, O, K,) A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who withholds himself from the love,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blamable love, of a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who abstains from that which is indecorous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nazihu Aln~afosi","text_ar":"نَزِهُ النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN Zalifapu Aln~afosi","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ ظَلِفَةُ النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaziyzapN Einoda nafosihaA","text_ar":"عَزِيزَةٌ عِنْدَ نَفْسِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman strong to resist, in her own estimation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and therefore meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who abstains from that which is indecorous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"Golius renders it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mulier pudica, et de honore suo sollicita"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifapN","text_ar":"ظَلِفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["M","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27632","headword_ar":"ظُلَّفٌ","root":"Zlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of which the sing. is not mentioned: accord. to general analogy, the sing. should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaAlifN","text_ar":"ظَالِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuluwfN Zul~afN","text_ar":"ظُلُوفٌ ظُلَّفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hard"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zuluwf","text_ar":"ظُلُوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divided hoofs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O, K:) the latter word being a corroborative. (S, O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}